'''賴東生'''綽號 '''「水房賴」'''黑幫[[和安樂|和安樂]]成員、澳門企業家，澳門[[菱峯集團|菱峯集團]]主席。

==生平==
興趣：賽車、潛水、滑雪<ref name="hkapple">{{Cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121202/18087925 |title=水房賴吹大雞　逼叠碼仔歸邊 |access-date=2014-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205024/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121202/18087925 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，目前主力投資澳門房地產、賭業賭廳、博彩中介人等生意<ref name="hkapple"/>，亦有參與中國大陸、中國澳門的慈善事業<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gdoverseaschn.com.cn/szqs/gyjx/200311120042.htm |title=澳门菱峰集团在珠海市斗门区开展慈善敬老活动 |access-date=2014-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140513205532/http://www.gdoverseaschn.com.cn/szqs/gyjx/200311120042.htm |archive-date=2014-05-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://10000xing.cn/x276/2013/0130103008.html |title=【赖氏网新闻】赖伟真宗长认捐叔颖公陵园建设资金100万元人民币 |access-date=2014-05-15 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126092343/http://10000xing.cn/x276/2013/0130103008.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
但賴東生亦被傳媒指是黑幫和安樂的頭目<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130822/00176_037.html |title=賴東生遭加國下驅逐令 |access-date=2014-05-14 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305005455/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130822/00176_037.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://vannewer.com/van/%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E3%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%BF%E8%B3%B4%E3%80%8D%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86/ |title=難民局取消「水房賴」公民身分 |access-date=2014-05-14 |archive-date=2014-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140514222450/http://vannewer.com/van/%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E3%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%BF%E8%B3%B4%E3%80%8D%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/13/8/21/n3945907.htm%E9%9A%B1%E5%B1%85%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B17%E5%B9%B4-%E8%B3%B4%E6%9D%B1%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-.html?p=all |title=隱居加國17年 賴東生將被拒入境 |access-date=2014-05-13 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304132238/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/13/8/21/n3945907.htm%E9%9A%B1%E5%B1%85%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B17%E5%B9%B4-%E8%B3%B4%E6%9D%B1%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-.html?p=all |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20130228/00407_079.html |title=黑幫買兇殺賴東生開價百萬 |access-date=2014-05-16 |archive-date=2019-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190908230238/http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20130228/00407_079.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賴東生更被傳媒指與在2011年出獄的「崩牙駒」[[尹國駒|尹國駒]]曾有利益衝突，賴氏曾下令暗殺尹氏<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130301/00176_035.html |title=賴東生涉曾下令暗殺尹國駒 |access-date=2014-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305075905/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130301/00176_035.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但近年來賴東生已趨向低調，據傳媒指出賴氏的家業達逾百億港幣<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/?aid=30447 |title=港澳江湖首富　控制過百賭廳　百億身家水房賴　豹隱20年首曝光 |access-date=2014-05-13 |archive-date=2016-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410033126/http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/?aid=30447 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
<br/>
2020年8月5日，香港媒體[[香港蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]消息，賴東生本人因涉及於中國大陸所犯的殺人案於[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]落網，預計日內會送回[[廣東省|廣東省]][[珠海市|珠海市]]送審行訊。<ref>[https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200805/PXDNFUSKMNVQXFR7OZMR6HAQ7Y/?fbclid=IwAR23ns8ur7zysWya-KUDdlFxbwuCC0oyQ87TABd4OvtvJZ17Mivue9JIziY 【獨家●黑幫被送中】澳門話事人「水房賴」柬埔寨落網 日內將被押回珠海]</ref>

